BUNK HOUSE COFFEE BAR
A safe space for ALL. We craft 100% Plant Based, Vegan, & mostly gluten free beverages, food, & baked goods. We believe in doing our part to cohesively thrive in a world where we harm no creature. We are VEGAN for our PLANET, our ANIMALS, & our HEALTH.

Here at Bunk House Coffee Bar, we make each beverage fresh to order. Each espresso shot is freshly ground and pulled for each individual drink. We offer a large selection of mylks so you’re sure to find the perfect one for you!
